snippet.title: Internet Vs Amber Heard
snippet.description:
If you're dense enough to not see this is a joke. Yes, it is, so please for the love of Christ don't cry in the comments about a shitpost made by some edgy wannabe YouTuber, K? K. 

Now on a serious note, This by no means is a joke with malicious intent especially towards the victim of Amber Herd's abuse Johnny Depp. This joke is satire on the situation regarding the internet lashing out and basically dealing mob justice against her career. And its clearly against someone who deserves it in every way. 

 But if you or a loved one are suffering from domestic abuse please go to this link https://www.thehotline.org/ thank you.
